Exception is an event which 'll cause Program termination.

try except else


try:
  which have the exact content
  
except:
  Exception message(This 'll be executed while error has occurred in try block)

When Exceptions can be used?
  It can be used while trying for a WebElement or a Text field which is something hidden.

When Multiple Exception block can be used?
  If the except block is written for particular Exception handling like zerodivisionerror then it handles only that particular Exception. 
  To handle other Exceptions separate Exception block has to be written.
  
try can be followed with except, else and finally block.
else block will be executed if the exception has not occurred.
finally block 
